Package: GUImorph
Type: Package
Title: Graphical User Interface for Morphometrics
Version: 0.10.0
Date: 2026-07-20
Author: Erik Otarola-Castillo  
Maintainer: Erik Otarola-Castillo <eoc@purdue.edu>
Description: GUI to R programs to digitize in 3D, conduct geometric morphometric
    analyses and plot results, based on OpenGL and Tk widgets. Runs on Windows
    and macOS; landmark, curve and surface semilandmark data are written in a
    format directly compatible with geomorph.
Imports:
    rgl,
    htmlwidgets,
    geomorph (>= 4.1.1),
    Morpho,
    parallel,      
    Rvcg,
    tcltk,
    tcltk2,
    vegan
Encoding: UTF-8
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    testthat
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
